Relationship adviser and blogger Joro Olumofin has shared the story of a paranoid man who claims his legally-married wife has been coming home without her panties. According to him, he suspects she might be cheating on him. He was able to list a couple of panties of hers that are presently nowhere to be found. The story has been cracking people up on social media with many helping him with ideas on strategies to help figure out the problem. Read his account below: Source